Package: mobian-tweaks
Architecture: all
Depends: dconf-gsettings-backend | gsettings-backend,
         dconf-cli,
         network-manager,
         umtp-responder,
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Special tweaks for Mobian
 Additional configuration files for Mobian, including:
   - default GNOME settings more suited to mobile devices
   - custom logind config, feedbackd profile and ModemManager polkit
     permissions
   - diverted desktop files for several applications
   - default environment variables for helping Qt apps and Firefox behave
     properly under Wayland
